text: "Run for Cover" is a 2001 song by English band Sugababes and is the third single from their debut studio album One Touch. It went to number 13 in the United Kingdom, number 17 in Scotland, number 49 in New Zealand and the Netherlands, number 28 in Germany, number 38 in Austria and number 35 in Ireland. ==Track listings== Notes * denotes additional producer(s) ==References== Category:2001 songs Category:Pop songs Category:Sugababes songs
